# Env var naming

Canonical names (see `.env.example`):

- `NUXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`, `NUXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`
- `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY`
- `NUXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL`
- `GEMINI_API_KEY`, `RESEND_API_KEY`, `RESEND_FROM_EMAIL`

`nuxt.config.ts` `supabase` block must map legacy aliases (`SUPABASE_URL`, `SUPABASE_KEY`, etc.) for `@nuxtjs/supabase` and `requireAdmin.ts`.

Adding a new var: update `.env.example`, `nuxt.config` runtimeConfig if needed, README — never commit `.env`.
